{"tid":1861732,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"AIA涉嫌歧視港人！中國客戶繳交保費deadline額外延長60天。中國客戶專享！香港人冇份啊！","createTime":"2020-02-04T09:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T17:35:14.000Z","uid":48040,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2619517aefcca03f2f840f161e06849a4132f8","tid":1861732,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"大家都知，保單若果遲交款，就會被終止，渣都冇得剩。<br />\n但原來保險公司只係對香港人先咁苛刻。<br />\n如果係中國客戶，就可以得到優待。<br />\nAIA宣布，中國客戶的保費繳交期限可以比香港人多60天wor。<br />\n唉，做香港人，生活係香港，偏偏被一間香港保險公司歧視，真係百般滋味在心頭啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5uK6bX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5uK6bX.jpg&h=045d1cef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WScQhiD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWScQhiD.jpg&h=dae38d4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：是否構成客戶歧視，由金管局及保監會去裁定啦！"},{"pid":"7cc099b2a5012643babbc0474f6ec0226da14bb0","tid":1861732,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cf895a04dd513c31fa90a090e9c7585973e1fd","tid":1861732,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545eb2d17577342d05bf69050cdc059f40fab3e7","tid":1861732,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09932d07c93828d85687041a8a549177a6c41667","tid":1861732,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"1、爭取香港客戶都可以寬限90天。<br />\n2、如果你係AIA客戶，如有需要，一定要充分利用你的寬限期啊"},{"pid":"213a0e98c1dd5ece0973f5c1b6be9f4b559030bd","tid":1861732,"uid":37303,"li